{
  "id": "adv_event_2311_01_04",
  "title": "限界なんて\n決めないで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "これからこのDVDを再生するから\n一緒に見てほしいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to play this DVD now‚\nso I want you to watch it with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_switch-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5500
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルの映像が始まったけど、これって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live battle footage has started‚ but this is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.325147438,
      "endTime": 12.0051475524,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリで\nうちらがサニピと対戦した時の映像やんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The footage from when we battled Sunny Peace\nin the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2184808571,
      "endTime": 17.934195121000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "この時のトリエルのパフォーマンスを見てどう思う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think of TRINITYAiLE’s performance at this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1341950256,
      "endTime": 22.642539485100002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "どうって……想いのこもった、いいパフォーマンスや\n見てると心が高ぶって、胸が熱くなってくるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean… It’s a good performance‚ full of emotion.\nMy heart races and my chest feels warm watching it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8492060183,
      "endTime": 32.5947845934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の緊張感を思い出すわね。サニピと\n競い合うことで、私達は実力以上の力を発揮出来た……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It brings back the tension of that time. By competing\nwith Sunny Peace‚ we were able to perform beyond our abilities…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7947844027,
      "endTime": 41.030838632400005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達は負けた。勝負は結果が全て\nどんなにいいパフォーマンスでも負けたら意味がないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we lost. In a competition‚ results are everything.\nNo matter how good the performance is‚ it’s meaningless if you lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3041711011,
      "endTime": 50.592266384599995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……本当に、そうなのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is that really true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.805599737,
      "endTime": 54.447958087800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "実は{user}さんから\n渡されたものがあるの。これ、読んでみて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ {user}-san\ngave me something. Here‚ read this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.6612913686,
      "endTime": 60.975214059900004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "今度はなんやの？\n……これは、アンケート用紙の束？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it this time?\n…This is… a bunch of questionnaires?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1752142506,
      "endTime": 67.9333323161,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2591.4513987999967
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルはファンミーティングを開催した時に\n必ずお客さんにアンケートをとるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever TRINITYAiLE holds a fan meeting‚\nwe always conduct a survey with our fans‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2652176139,
      "endTime": 74.81229221790001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは今までのアンケートを\n全部保管してくれてたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san kept all the questionnaires\nfrom all the past meetings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0122923133,
      "endTime": 80.3747865912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに見覚えがあるわね、懐かしいわ……\nでも、これとさっきの映像になんの関係があるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember seeing these. It’s nostalgic…\nBut what does this have to do with the footage we just watched?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5614532389,
      "endTime": 88.9140607751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "アンケートに「トリエルの活動で一番印象に残っている\n出来事はなんですか？」っていう質問があるでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The questionnaire asks‚ “What is the most memorable event\nfrom TRINITYAiLE’s activities?” right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1740595099,
      "endTime": 97.5087990042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 97.8821306782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　この質問の答え……\nこの人も、こっちの人も、みんな同じ答えや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? The answers to this question…\nThis person‚ that person‚ they all have the same answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2821311868,
      "endTime": 107.4333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの人達が、トリエルの活動で\n一番印象に残ってる出来事は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The event that our fans remember the most\nfrom all of our activities is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7022688464,
      "endTime": 113.5333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "「NEXT VENUSグランプリ準決勝\nサニーピースとのライブバトル」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“The NEXT VENUS Grand Prix semifinals‚\nthe live battle with Sunny Peace.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7956033624,
      "endTime": 119.6619070924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "私達、沢山イベントに出て、グラビアやTVCMも\nやってライブバトルだって99連勝もしたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve been in a lot of events‚ done gravure and TV commercials‚\nand even achieved 99th straight win in live battles‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8685735301,
      "endTime": 128.8068505839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、ファンのみんなが思う\nトリエルが一番輝いてた瞬間は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the moment that our fans think\nTRINITYAiLE shined the brightest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0068503932,
      "endTime": 135.2666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "最高のライバルと競い合って\n持てる力を全部出し切って歌った時なんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is when we competed against our greatest rival\nand sang with all our might.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5395797328,
      "endTime": 142.02586093690002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "99連勝した時より、サニピに負けた時の方が\n私達は輝いてたって言うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re saying that we shined brighter when we lost to Sunny Peace\nthan when we achieved 99th straight win?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.2391943848,
      "endTime": 149.3991945183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ、ファンは勝敗じゃなくて私達を見てるんだよ\nトリエルの在り方から勇気をもらってるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ the fans are looking at us‚ not at wins or losses.\nThey’re getting courage from how TRINITYAiLE is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.605860956,
      "endTime": 160.4805317476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もっと挑戦しよう\n限界なんて決めないで、ギリギリまで力を出し尽くそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ let’s challenge ourselves more.\nLet’s not set any limits‚ let’s push ourselves to the limit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.6738650238,
      "endTime": 169.251688472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そうすればトリエルはもっともっと輝ける……\nファンのみんなも、そんなトリエルを見たいんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we do that‚ TRINITYAiLE will shine even brighter…\nAnd that’s what our fans want to see!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4383553103,
      "endTime": 179.6645472527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "……私は勝つことにこだわり過ぎて\n大切なことを忘れていたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I was so focused on winning\nthat I forgot what was important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.0880848483,
      "endTime": 188.2827334001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんに教えられたわ。ごめんなぁ\nほんまはうちらが気付かなあかんかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You taught me a lesson‚ Sumire-chan. I’m sorry.\nWe should have realized it ourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.4894001241,
      "endTime": 195.7427106139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_04-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "私の方こそ、うまく言葉に出来なくてごめんね\n言いたかったこと、ちゃんと伝わったかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry I couldn’t put it into words very well.\nDid you understand what I wanted to say…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.9493772424,
      "endTime": 205.64520453580002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
